	<description>
		<p>ImageFan Reloaded features mouse and key-based interaction using:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>left mouse button for interacting with tabs and folders, and for selecting, opening, zooming in and out, and dragging images</li>
			<li>right mouse button for returning from the opened image to the main view</li>
			<li>mouse wheel for scrolling through folders and thumbnails, and for navigating back and forward through opened images</li>
			<li>key Tab for cycling through active tabs</li>
			<li>key R for toggling recursive folder access, and key combo Shift-R for toggling persistent recursive folder access</li>
			<li>keys W-A-S-D, Up-Down-Left-Right, Backspace-Space and PageUp-PageDown for back and forward navigation through thumbnails and opened images</li>
			<li>key Enter for entering image view and zoomed image view modes</li>
			<li>key I for toggling image info in image view and zoomed image view modes</li>
			<li>keys Esc and T for exiting image view and zoomed image view modes</li>
			<li>key Esc for quitting application</li>
			<li>key F1 for displaying About view</li>
		</ul>
	</description>

